    "The operation p produces the parent of a node, and the operation c produces the set of a node's immediate children.",
    "D, implied by [7, Claims A.14 and A.15] and c(v) denotes the set of D immediate children of v. Figure 2:2Figure2: a) The approximation ratios obtained with directly optimized parameters, parameter setting method of Ref."
